$SOL
With \(a_n = $an\), 
\[ \sqrt[n]{a_n} = \sqrt[n]{$an} = \left( 1 + \frac{1}{$a n} \right)^{$exp} \] and \[ \lim_{n \to \infty} \sqrt[n]{a_n} = $result. \]
Therefore, $FinalState


